title: Super bowl 2021
description: The Super Bowl is the annual playoff championship game of the National Football League (NFL). It has served as the final game of every NFL season since 1966, replacing the NFL Championship Game.

title: Rihanna concert
description: Rihanna became an instant sensation after Jay-Z signed her to Def Jam Records in 2005. Her debut tour kicked off in 2006 and she toured every year until 2014. She returned to the road in 2016 with the Anti World Tour and has since grown her empire in music, fashion, and cosmetics. To date, she has performed over 500 concerts in 50 different countries across 7 tours.
